    <item>
      <title>普利兹克在因沟通失败而发泄不满后支持拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/pritzker-backs-biden-after-venting-over-failure-to-communicate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. Pritzker 表示，他支持乔·拜登连任，在最初对拜登提出慎重批评之后，他加入了其他民选官员的支持行列，转而支持这位陷入困境的总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/pritzker-backs-biden-after-venting-over-failure-to-communicate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的前总理寻求中右翼联盟组建政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/macron-s-ex-premier-seeks-center-right-accord-to-form-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的前总理爱德华·菲利普呼吁中间派和中右翼政党联合起来组建新政府，因为在提前选举导致法国议会严重分裂之后，政治角逐愈演愈烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/macron-s-ex-premier-seeks-center-right-accord-to-form-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约将增强乌克兰的防空能力并派遣 F-16</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-set-to-boost-ukraine-s-air-defenses-and-send-f-16s</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约国家将向乌克兰提供 F-16 战斗机和新的防空系统，以对抗俄罗斯加强的导弹袭击，尽管最新的评估表明冲突正走向无限期的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/nato-set-to-boost-ukraine-s-air-defenses-and-send-f-16s</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 19:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑莉释放代表，敦促他们在大会上支持特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/haley-releases-delegates-urges-them-to-back-trump-at-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[妮基·黑利 (Nikki Haley) 释放了她的代表，并鼓励他们在下周的共和党全国代表大会上支持她曾经的主要竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/haley-releases-delegates-urges-them-to-back-trump-at-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国称鲍勃·梅内德斯“权利”导致现金、黄金贿赂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bob-menendez-showed-entitlement-in-seeking-out-bribes-us-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，在对美国参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯的腐败案审判中，检察官向陪审员辩称，他收受了现金、金条和一辆奔驰车等贿赂，同时承诺帮助埃及商人和国家，这是“理所当然”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bob-menendez-showed-entitlement-in-seeking-out-bribes-us-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:38:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦为拜登辩护，称其在包括与中国习近平在内的多次长时间会谈中“极其高效”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，她的老板总统乔·拜登在长时间的会议中“极其高效”，并在周二回答有关其精神敏锐度的问题时为他辩护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>知情人士称 Siddiq 将出任英国城市事务大臣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命图利普·西迪克 (Tulip Siddiq) 为英国金融城大臣，该职位属于财政部，将让她成为监管和倡导关键金融服务行业的核心人物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/tulip-siddiq-to-be-uk-s-city-minister-person-familiar-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分裂的民主党人抨击特朗普议程以转移拜登的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管国会民主党人周二就是否支持乔·拜登参选展开争论，但白宫和立法者还是掌握了统一的策略：试图将话题从总统的敏锐思维转移到唐纳德·特朗普的政策目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/biden-slows-democratic-defections-while-election-worries-persist</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 14:56:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管受到中国劳工质疑，太阳能公司仍获美国数百万美元税收抵免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-09/south-korean-solar-company-secures-us-tax-credits-despite-chinese-labor-question</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国韩华集团表示，已采取措施确保其位于佐治亚州的 Qcells 工厂的供应链完整性。但该公司从其供应商因在中国存在强迫劳动而受到美国官员制裁的公司采购材料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-09/south-korean-solar-company-secures-us-tax-credits-despite-chinese-labor-question</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 04:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
